short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Discover the world of Muichiro Tokito, the Mist Hashira from Demon Slayer, every time you open a new tab.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This Chrome extension brings the character of Muichiro Tokito to your browser with stunning visuals and interactive features. Customize your new tab page with beautiful, high-quality images of the Mist Hashira, along with inspirational quotes and reminders of his unwavering resolve.

Get an immersive experience as you enjoy every moment spent on your browser. Stay motivated with Muichiro's words of wisdom and discover new backgrounds and artwork that celebrate his journey in the Demon Slayer universe. Whether you're a fan of the series or simply admire his calm strength, this extension is a must-have for any Demon Slayer enthusiast.

Transform your browser into a tribute to Muichiro Tokito and carry his spirit with you wherever you go. Enhance your browsing experience today!
